counters update automatically. Milestone messages celebrate achievements at 7, 14, 30, 100, and 365 days.\"},{\"icon\":\"calendar_month\",\"title\":\"Calendar heatmap visualization\",\"description\":\"A 30-day heatmap on each habit card shows your recent consistency at a glance. Completed days are highlighted in the habit's color.\"},{\"icon\":\"event_repeat\",\"title\":\"Flexible scheduling (daily, weekly, specific days)\",\"description\":\"Set habits as daily, specific weekdays, or a target number of times per week. The streak calculator accounts for non-scheduled days.\"},{\"icon\":\"drag_indicator\",\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop habit reordering\",\"description\":\"Reorder habits by dragging them into your preferred order. Position changes persist to the database automatically.\"},{\"icon\":\"cloud_sync\",\"title\":\"Cloud sync with authentication\",\"description\":\"Email/password and Google sign-in keep your data synced across devices. All habits and logs are stored securely in the cloud.\"},{\"icon\":\"insights\",\"title\":\"Progress insights and analytics\",\"description\":\"A dedicated insights page shows completion rates, streak data, and progress visualizations across all your habits.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Habit creation with custom colors\",\"description\":\"Create habits with a name, description, and color from a curated palette. Each habit card is visually distinct so your dashboard is easy to scan.\"},{\"title\":\"Streak tracking with milestones\",\"description\":\"Current and longest streak counters update automatically. Milestone messages celebrate achievements at 7, 14, 21, 30, 50, 100, 200, and 365 days.\"},{\"title\":\"Calendar heatmap\",\"description\":\"A 30-day heatmap on each habit card shows your recent consistency at a glance. Completed days are highlighted in the habit's color.\"},{\"title\":\"Flexible frequency scheduling\",\"description\":\"Set habits as daily, specific weekdays (e.g. Mon/Wed/Fri), or a target number of times per week. The streak calculator accounts for non-scheduled days.\"},{\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop reordering\",\"description\":\"Reorder habits by dragging them into your preferred order. Position changes persist to the database automatically.\"},{\"title\":\"Insights and analytics\",\"description\":\"A dedicated insights page shows completion rates, streak data, and progress visualizations across all your habits.\"},{\"title\":\"Cloud sync with authentication\",\"description\":\"Email/password and Google sign-in keep your data synced across devices. All habits and logs are stored securely in the cloud.\"},{\"title\":\"Onboarding flow\",\"description\":\"New users are guided through creating their first habits with a clean, step-by-step onboarding experience.\"},{\"title\":\"Settings and data management\",\"description\":\"Manage your account, clear all data, or sign out from the settings page.\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive design\",\"description\":\"Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile with a bottom navigation bar optimized for mobile use.\"},{\"title\":\"Dark mode support\",\"description\":\"Full dark mode with carefully tuned colors that match the app's calm, focused aesthetic.\"},{\"title\":\"Reminder times\",\"description\":\"Set optional reminder times for each habit to help you stay on track throughout the day.\"}],\"content\":\"$39\",\"relativePath\":\"continuum-daily-habit-tracker-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"ecommerce-store-1\",\"id\":\"ecommerce-store-1\",\"title\":\"Ecommerce Store Website Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"a8e59680-e4fc-4735-a797-36af2f7e2875\",\"url\":\"https://linea-jewelry.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Launch a luxury jewelry store with editorial-grade product showcases and complete checkout flow. Professional design, mobile-optimized browsing, and premium brand presentation—go live in hours, not weeks.\",\"tagline\":\"Premium design for webstore\",\"description\":\"This template gives you a complete jewelry e-commerce store that