r device and place them on the canvas. Drag to reposition, resize with handles, and rotate with corner controls.\"},{\"icon\":\"auto_awesome\",\"title\":\"AI image generation\",\"description\":\"Generate images from text prompts using the built-in AI tool. Created images appear directly on your canvas ready to arrange.\"},{\"icon\":\"text_fields\",\"title\":\"Text annotations\",\"description\":\"Add text items to your canvas for notes, labels, or captions. Double-click to edit text in place.\"},{\"icon\":\"dashboard\",\"title\":\"Multiple board management\",\"description\":\"Create and manage multiple boards from a central dashboard. Each board shows a thumbnail preview, title, and last-updated timestamp.\"},{\"icon\":\"keyboard\",\"title\":\"Keyboard shortcuts and undo/redo\",\"description\":\"Full undo/redo stack and power-user shortcuts for select, copy, paste, delete, zoom, and pan.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Infinite spatial canvas\",\"description\":\"Place images and text anywhere on a zoomable, pannable canvas with a subtle dot grid background.\"},{\"title\":\"Image upload and placement\",\"description\":\"Upload images from your device and place them on the canvas. Drag to reposition, resize with handles, and rotate with corner controls.\"},{\"title\":\"AI image generation\",\"description\":\"Generate images from text prompts using the built-in AI tool. Created images appear directly on your canvas ready to arrange.\"},{\"title\":\"Text annotations\",\"description\":\"Add text items to your canvas for notes, labels, or captions. Double-click to edit text in place.\"},{\"title\":\"Multi-board dashboard\",\"description\":\"Create and manage multiple boards from a central dashboard. Each board shows a thumbnail preview, title, and last-updated timestamp.\"},{\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop reordering\",\"description\":\"Reorder boards on the dashboard with drag-and-drop. On the canvas, freely move and arrange all items.\"},{\"title\":\"Copy and paste\",\"descript