ose from multiple variations without leaving the editor.\"},{\"icon\":\"aspect_ratio\",\"title\":\"Multiple format presets (square, vertical, landscape, story)\",\"description\":\"Choose from square (1:1), vertical (4:5), landscape (16:9), and story/reel (9:16) formats with platform-specific dimensions.\"},{\"icon\":\"cloud_upload\",\"title\":\"Image and video upload with progress tracking\",\"description\":\"Upload images and videos with progress tracking. See how your media will crop on each platform's aspect ratio.\"},{\"icon\":\"text_fields\",\"title\":\"Character count enforcement per platform\",\"description\":\"Real-time character counters for each platform (X 280, Instagram 2200, LinkedIn 3000, Facebook 63206) with visual warnings.\"},{\"icon\":\"save\",\"title\":\"Draft saving and management\",\"description\":\"Posts are saved as drafts in the cloud. Return to unfinished content anytime from any device.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Multi-platform live preview\",\"description\":\"See your post rendered as it would appear on Instagram, LinkedIn, X, and Facebook — updating in real time as you type.\"},{\"title\":\"Format presets\",\"description\":\"Choose from square (1:1), vertical (4:5), landscape (16:9), and story/reel (9:16) formats with platform-specific dimensions.\"},{\"title\":\"AI text enhancement\",\"description\":\"Get AI-generated suggestions to improve your post copy. Choose from multiple variations without leaving the editor.\"},{\"title\":\"Image and video upload\",\"description\":\"Upload images and videos with progress tracking. See how your media will crop on each platform's aspect ratio.\"},{\"title\":\"Character count enforcement\",\"description\":\"Real-time character counters for each platform with visual warnings when approaching or exceeding limits.\"},{\"title\":\"Draft saving\",\"description\":\"Posts are saved as drafts in the cloud. Return to unfinished content anytime from any device.\"},{\"title\":\"Profile customization\",\"des