\",\"description\":\"Custom-styled video player with featured project display, modestbranding, and professional presentation for client work examples\"},{\"title\":\"Intelligent Image Fallback System\",\"description\":\"Automatic Unsplash CDN fallbacks with lazy loading ensuring images always display beautifully even when primary sources fail\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive Grid Layout System\",\"description\":\"CSS Grid and Flexbox combinations adapting from single-column mobile to four-column desktop layouts for optimal content presentation\"},{\"title\":\"Smooth Scroll Navigation Experience\",\"description\":\"Hardware-accelerated anchor-based navigation with fixed sticky header that transitions to backdrop-blur on scroll for better readability\"},{\"title\":\"Premium Typography Hierarchy\",\"description\":\"Bagel Fat One display font with fluid type scales and optimized character variants ensuring exceptional readability across screen sizes\"},{\"title\":\"Mobile Hamburger Menu System\",\"description\":\"Right-side slide-in panel with spring animations, body scroll lock, and auto-close on scroll for intuitive mobile navigation\"},{\"title\":\"Dark Mode Ready Architecture\",\"description\":\"Complete CSS variable system with light and dark theme definitions enabling instant theme switching for future enhancements\"},{\"title\":\"Semantic HTML Structure\",\"description\":\"ARIA labels, proper heading hierarchy, and semantic elements ensuring accessibility compliance and improved SEO performance\"},{\"title\":\"Component-Based Scalability\",\"description\":\"Modular React architecture with TypeScript interfaces and 65+ shadcn/ui components providing unlimited expansion potential for growing businesses\"}],\"content\":\"$40\",\"relativePath\":\"visual-landing-page-1.md\"},{\"slug\":\"dealflow-visual-crm-pipeline-tracker-template\",\"id\":\"dealflow-visual-crm-pipeline-tracker-template\",\"title\":\"Dealflow\",\"pageTitle\":\"Dealflow - Visual CRM \u0026 Pipeline Tracker Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"55cb9453-4733-49db-aef5-06979162c0cb\",\"url\":\"https://thepipelineiq.lovable.app/\",\"subtitle\":\"Visual pipeline board with drag-and-drop deals, activity logging, forecasting, and CSV import/export\",\"description\":\"Track sales deals across pipeline stages with a visual Kanban board. Drag-and-drop deal cards, log activities, manage contacts and companies, forecast revenue, and import/export data — all in one CRM template.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Dealflow - Visual CRM \u0026 Pipeline Tracker Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Track sales deals across pipeline stages with a visual Kanban board. Drag-and-drop deal cards, log activities, manage contacts and companies, forecast revenue, and import/export data — all in one CRM template.\",\"subcategory\":\"internal-tools\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/dealflow.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/dealflow.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/dealflow.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"templates\",\"dashboard-templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"drag_indicator\",\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop pipeline board\",\"description\":\"Move deals between stages visually and see your full sales funnel update in real time.\"},{\"icon\":\"credit_card\",\"title\":\"Deal cards with key metrics\",\"description\":\"Every card shows value, expected close date, contact, company, and current stage without extra clicks.\"},{\"icon\":\"bar_chart\",\"title\":\"Dashboard with pipeline analytics\",\"description\":\"See total deals, pipeline value, win rate, and average sales cycle at a glance — filterable by week, month, quarter, or all time.\"},{\"icon\":\"people\",\"title\":\"Contact \u0026 company management\",\"description\":\"Store and search contacts with tags, positions, and company associations. Manage company accounts with industry, website, and linked contacts.\"},{\"icon\":\"calendar_month\",\"title\":\"Activity logging \u0026 calendar\",\"description\":\"Log calls, emails, meetings, and notes against contacts and deals. View all activities, tasks, and deal close dates on a monthly calendar.\"},{\"icon\":\"file_download\",\"title\":\"CSV import \u0026 export\",\"description\":\"Bulk import contacts and deals from CSV with column mapping, or export your data to CSV. Downloadable templates included.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop pipeline board\",\"description\":\"Move deals between stages visually with drag interactions and instant board updates.\"},{\"title\":\"Customizable deal stages\",\"description\":\"Rename, reorder, add, or remove pipeline stages to match your actual sales process through the onboarding wizard or settings.\"},{\"title\":\"Deal value and close date tracking\",\"description\":\"Every deal card displays its value, expected close date, probability, contact, and company so you can prioritize at a glance.\"},{\"title\":\"Dashboard with KPI cards\",\"description\":\"See total deals, pipeline value, win rate, and average sales cycle — filterable by this week, month, quarter, or all time. Includes recent activity feed and deals closing soon.\"},{\"title\":\"Revenue forecasting\",\"description\":\"Six-month weighted revenue projection based on deal values, probabilities, and expected close dates.\"},{\"title\":\"Contact management\",\"description\":\"Create, search, tag, and manage contacts with email, phone, position, and company association. Bulk select and delete supported.\"},{\"title\":\"Company management\",\"description\":\"Track company accounts with industry, website, and linked contact counts. Search and bulk operations included.\"},{\"title\":\"Activity logging\",\"description\":\"Log calls, emails, meetings, and notes linked to contacts and deals. Filter by activity type and bulk delete.\"},{\"title\":\"Task management\",\"description\":\"Create tasks with priorities (high, medium, low), due dates, and links to deals or contacts. Filter by status and priority.\"},{\"title\":\"Calendar view\",\"description\":\"Monthly calendar showing activities, task due dates, and deal close dates with day-detail sidebar and popover previews.\"},{\"title\":\"CSV import \u0026 export\",\"description\":\"Bulk import contacts and deals from CSV with column mapping and validation. Export contacts and deals to CSV. Downloadable CSV templates included.\"},{\"title\":\"Pipeline chart visualization\",\"description\":\"View deal distribution and value across stages with bar charts and pie charts in the reports section.\"},{\"title\":\"Global search\",\"description\":\"Search across deals, contacts, and companies from the top bar.\"},{\"title\":\"Notification center\",\"description\":\"In-app notification center with read/unread state for deal movements and task reminders.\"},{\"title\":\"Onboarding wizard\",\"description\":\"Guided setup flow for new users — enter company name, team size, and customize pipeline stages before launching.\"},{\"title\":\"Settings \u0026 configuration\",\"description\":\"Profile management (name, avatar), pipeline stage customization, team member management, notification preferences, email template editor, and external connector setup.\"},{\"title\":\"Authentication\",\"description\":\"Full email-based authentication with sign up, sign in, and session management. Email verification required.\"},{\"title\":\"Dark mode support\",\"description\":\"Toggle between light and dark themes across the entire application.\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive layout\",\"description\":\"Sidebar navigation with collapsible menu. Adapts to desktop, tablet, and mobile screen sizes.\"},{\"title\":\"Team collaboration\",\"description\":\"All users on a team can view and manage deals, contacts, companies, and activities. Single-tenant architecture with shared data access.\"}],\"content\":\"$41\",\"relativePath\":\"dealflow-visual-crm-pipeline-tracker-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"clean-photographer\",\"id\":\"clean-photographer-portfolio\",\"title\":\"Photographer portfolio\",\"pageTitle\":\"Clean Photographer — Photography Portfolio Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"c2183e99-2926-417a-95b8-ff67a5421501\",\"url\":\"https://clean-photographer.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Launch a photography portfolio that attracts premium clients without design skills. Gallery layouts, category organization, and fast performance—ready to showcase your work in hours.\",\"tagline\":\"Interactive image showcase\",\"description\":\"Launch a photography portfolio that attracts premium clients without design skills. Gallery layouts, category organization, and fast performance—ready to showcase your work in hours.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Clean Photographer - Photography Portfolio Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Launch a professional photography portfolio that attracts premium clients. Gallery layouts, category organization, and fast performance. No coding required.\",\"subcategory\":\"portfolio\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Portfolio\",\"Photography\",\"Minimalist\",\"Gallery\",\"Clean\",\"Modern\"],\"screenshot\":\"/templates/clean-photographer-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"/templates/clean-photographer-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"/templates/previews/clean-photographer-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#FFFFFF\",\"#000000\",\"#F8F8F8\",\"#E5E5E5\",\"#333333\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"is_partner_template\":false,\"date\":\"2025-11-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"lastModified\":\"2025-11-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"expand\",\"title\":\"Clean Minimalist Design\",\"description\":\"Spacious layouts with plenty of whitespace that let your photography speak for itself\"},{\"icon\":\"image_stack\",\"title\":\"Elegant Galleries\",\"description\":\"Beautiful image galleries with smooth transitions and intuitive navigation\"},{\"icon\":\"devices\",\"title\":\"Fully Responsive\",\"description\":\"Seamless viewing experience across all devices with optimized mobile layouts\"},{\"icon\":\"bolt\",\"title\":\"Fast \u0026 Lightweight\",\"description\":\"Optimized performance with fast loading times for the best user experience\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Fully Responsive \u0026 Mobile-First\",\"description\":\"Fluid gallery layouts optimized for phones, tablets, and desktops with touch gestures for smooth image browsing\"},{\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance\",\"description\":\"Optimized image loading with lazy loading, code splitting, and CDN-ready architecture for sub-2s load times\"},{\"title\":\"Premium UI Component Library\",\"description\":\"100+ pre-built components with Radix UI primitives and Shadcn/UI styling for professional presentation\"},{\"title\":\"SEO \u0026 Meta Optimization\",\"description\":\"Pre-configured meta tags, Open Graph cards for social sharing, and structured data for photography portfolios\"},{\"title\":\"Accessibility Excellence (WCAG 2.1 AA)\",\"description\":\"Semantic HTML5, ARIA labels, keyboard navigation, and screen reader support for inclusive portfolio access\"},{\"title\":\"Advanced Form Handling\",\"description\":\"Client inquiry forms with validation, real-time error feedback, and file upload for booking requests\"}],\"content\":\"$42\",\"relativePath\":\"clean-photographer.md\"},{\"slug\":\"expensedesk-expense-reporting-approval-tool-template\",\"id\":\"expensedesk-expense-reporting-approval-tool-template\",\"title\":\"ExpenseDesk\",\"pageTitle\":\"ExpenseDesk - Expense Reporting \u0026 Approval Tool Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"80eb6fbb-fbd3-498e-a8d8-8486ce9a2dda\",\"url\":\"https://expensedesk.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Centralized expense submission, approval workflows, and reimbursement tracking\",\"description\":\"Submit, review, and approve expense claims with receipt uploads, category tagging, and multi-step approval workflows. Full audit trail, AI assistant, and spending analytics built in.\",\"metaTitle\":\"ExpenseDesk - Expense reporting \u0026 approval tool template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Submit, review, and approve expense claims with receipt uploads, category tagging, and multi-step approval workflows. Full audit trail, AI assistant, and spending analytics built in.\",\"subcategory\":\"internal-tools\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/expense_deck.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/expense_deck.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/expense_deck.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"templates\",\"dashboard-templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"receipt_long\",\"title\":\"Expense submission with receipt uploads\",\"description\":\"Employees submit claims with photos or scans of receipts, category tags, and notes from a guided form that captures everything finance needs.\"},{\"icon\":\"approval\",\"title\":\"Multi-step approval workflows\",\"description\":\"Claims route through manager review and finance approval in a two-step process, so every expense follows your organization's sign-off process.\"},{\"icon\":\"label\",\"title\":\"Manual category tagging\",\"description\":\"Employees select from predefined expense categories when submitting, keeping reports consistent and spending organized by type.\"},{\"icon\":\"track_changes\",\"title\":\"Real-time status tracking\",\"description\":\"Submitters see exactly where their claim is in the approval pipeline — draft, submitted, manager approved, approved, rejected, or reimbursed.\"},{\"icon\":\"history\",\"title\":\"Full audit trail\",\"description\":\"Every action on a claim is logged with timestamps and user details, giving finance teams a complete compliance record.\"},{\"icon\":\"bar_chart\",\"title\":\"Spending analytics dashboard\",\"description\":\"Break down spending by category, cost center, time period, or merchant to spot trends and control costs across the organization.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Expense submission form with receipt uploads\",\"description\":\"A guided form where employees enter amount, date, merchant, category, cost center, notes, and attach receipt photos or scans.\"},{\"title\":\"Manual expense categorization\",\"description\":\"Employees select from predefined categories when submitting expenses, keeping data consistent and reports organized.\"},{\"title\":\"Two-step approval workflow\",\"description\":\"Claims route through manager review first, then finance sign-off, following a fixed two-step approval chain.\"},{\"title\":\"Real-time claim status tracking\",\"description\":\"Submitters see their claim's current status at every stage — draft, submitted, manager approved, approved, rejected, or reimbursed — with a visual progress indicator.\"},{\"title\":\"Manager approval dashboard\",\"description\":\"Managers see all pending claims for their team with amounts, dates, and expense details in one view, with one-click approve or reject.\"},{\"title\":\"Finance review and batch processing\",\"description\":\"Finance teams get a unified queue of all expenses with batch approve, reject, and mark-as-reimbursed actions.\"},{\"title\":\"Full audit trail\",\"description\":\"Every action on every claim is logged with timestamp, user, and details for complete compliance and accountability.\"},{\"title\":\"Spending analytics dashboard\",\"description\":\"Break down expenses by category, cost center, status, time period, or merchant with visual charts, cumulative spending trends, and filterable time ranges.\"},{\"title\":\"AI expense assistant\",\"description\":\"Ask natural-language questions about your expense data — spending patterns, category breakdowns, approval statuses, or specific transactions — with streaming AI responses.\"},{\"title\":\"Cost center tracking\",\"description\":\"Assign expenses to cost centers to track spending by department or project.\"},{\"title\":\"Role-based access control\",\"description\":\"Three roles with distinct permissions — employees submit, managers approve for their team, finance processes organization-wide.\"},{\"title\":\"CSV import and export\",\"description\":\"Import expenses in bulk from CSV files and export expense data for accounting software or record-keeping.\"},{\"title\":\"Draft and submit workflow\",\"description\":\"Save expenses as drafts and submit them later, giving employees flexibility to complete claims when ready.\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive design across devices\",\"description\":\"Submit expenses from your phone after a business dinner, or review approvals on your laptop at your desk.\"}],\"content\":\"$43\",\"relativePath\":\"expensedesk-expense-reporting-approval-tool-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"hobby-photographer\",\"id\":\"hobby-photographer-portfolio\",\"title\":\"Personal portfolio\",\"pageTitle\":\"Hobby Photographer — Personal Photography Portfolio Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"96ce7324-2bfa-401f-a87d-7eb158e7b479\",\"url\":\"https://hobby-photographer-template.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Launch a professional photography portfolio that attracts paying clients. Full-screen galleries, category organization, and contact forms—ready to deploy in hours, not weeks.\",\"tagline\":\"Personal work showcase\",\"description\":\"Launch a professional photography portfolio that attracts paying clients. Full-screen galleries, category organization, and contact forms—ready to deploy in hours, not weeks.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Photography Portfolio Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Launch a professional photography portfolio in hours, not weeks. Custom-built look without developer costs. Full-screen galleries, client contact forms, mobile-ready.\",\"subcategory\":\"portfolio\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Portfolio\",\"Photography\",\"Hobby\",\"Personal\",\"Amateur\",\"Casual\"],\"screenshot\":\"/templates/hobby-photographer-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"/templates/hobby-photographer-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"/templates/previews/hobby-photographer-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#FFFFFF\",\"#2C2C2C\",\"#F0F0F0\",\"#E0E0E0\",\"#444444\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2025-11-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"lastModified\":\"2025-11-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"image_stack\",\"title\":\"Professional Image Showcase System\",\"description\":\"Full-screen lightbox galleries with keyboard navigation designed for photographers presenting client work professionally\"},{\"icon\":\"gauge\",\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance Optimized\",\"description\":\"Sub-2 second load times with lazy loading, code splitting, and optimized images for immediate visual impact\"},{\"icon\":\"devices\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Design\",\"description\":\"Pixel-perfect layouts across all devices ensuring your photography looks stunning on every screen size\"},{\"icon\":\"half_moon\",\"title\":\"Dark Mode With System Detection\",\"description\":\"Automatic theme switching respects visitor preferences while maintaining professional aesthetic across both modes\"},{\"icon\":\"check_circle\",\"title\":\"Zero Technical Maintenance Required\",\"description\":\"Static architecture with optimized assets means no server management, updates, or technical overhead costs\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Interactive Lightbox Gallery\",\"description\":\"Full-screen image viewing with touch gestures, keyboard navigation, and smooth fade transitions for professional portfolio presentations that keep visitors engaged\"},{\"title\":\"Interactive Project Previews\",\"description\":\"When visitors hover over your project thumbnails, images smoothly zoom and display project details, creating an engaging browsing experience that showcases your work professionally\"},{\"title\":\"Smart Contact Form\",\"description\":\"Your contact form automatically checks that visitors fill out required fields correctly (like valid email addresses), showing helpful error messages if something's wrong and a confirmation when their message sends successfully\"},{\"title\":\"Smart Navigation Menu\",\"description\":\"Your menu starts transparent over your images and becomes solid as visitors scroll down, keeping it easy to find while looking beautiful at the top of your page\"},{\"title\":\"Swipe Through Photos on Mobile\",\"description\":\"Visitors can naturally swipe left and right to browse your gallery photos on phones and tablets, just like they're used to in their favorite photo apps\"},{\"title\":\"Keyboard-Friendly Navigation\",\"description\":\"Visitors who use keyboards instead of mice (including those with accessibility needs) can easily navigate through your galleries and menus, making your portfolio welcoming to everyone\"}],\"content\":\"$44\",\"relativePath\":\"hobby-photographer.md\"},{\"slug\":\"quotekit-proposal-quote-generator-template\",\"id\":\"quotekit-proposal-quote-generator-template\",\"title\":\"QuoteKit\",\"pageTitle\":\"QuoteKit - Proposal \u0026 Quote Generator Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"4501d5af-6bb0-44fa-bba5-e044ef715622\",\"url\":\"https://quotekit.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Create branded proposals with AI-assisted content, reusable templates, and secure one-link client s