\",\"title\":\"Engagement tracking\",\"description\":\"Know when a client opens and views your proposal in real time via logged view events.\"},{\"icon\":\"picture_as_pdf\",\"title\":\"PDF export\",\"description\":\"Generate a downloadable PDF of any proposal, ready to send or archive.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Reusable proposal templates\",\"description\":\"Save templates for your common services, organized by category, and generate new proposals by selecting a template and customizing.\"},{\"title\":\"AI-powered content generation\",\"description\":\"Generate section content with built-in AI assistance directly inside the proposal builder.\"},{\"title\":\"Multi-step proposal builder\",\"description\":\"A five-step guided flow — template, client, content, pricing, review — keeps proposal creation structured and complete.\"},{\"title\":\"Line-item editor with quantities, prices, and discounts\",\"description\":\"Add, remove, and reorder deliverables with per-unit pricing, quantity fields, and per-item discount percentages.\"},{\"title\":\"Automatic subtotals, taxes, and grand totals\",\"description\":\"Totals calculate as you type so there are no spreadsheet formulas to maintain or manual math errors.\"},{\"title\":\"Secure link sharing with password and expiry\",\"description\":\"Share proposals via a unique URL with optional password protection and configurable expiration dates.\"},{\"title\":\"Engagement tracking\",\"description\":\"View events are logged when clients open shared proposals, so you know exactly when they've been seen.\"},{\"title\":\"Proposal status lifecycle\",\"description\":\"Proposals move through draft, sent, viewed, accepted, and rejected statuses with visual indicators throughout the app.\"},{\"title\":\"Client management\",\"description\":\"Maintain a searchable client directory with contact details, notes, and linked proposal history.\"},{\"title\":\"Role-based access control\",\"description\":\"Three roles — admin, manager, agent — control visibility and permissions across proposals, settings, and team management.\"},{\"title\":\"Dashboard with analytics\",\"description\":\"Real-time stats, trend charts, and recent proposal activity give you a snapshot of your pipeline and revenue.\"},{\"title\":\"Team and department management\",\"description\":\"Organize team members into departments and manage roles from the settings panel (admin only).\"},{\"title\":\"Organization branding\",\"description\":\"Set your company name, logo, website, and brand color once — they appear on every shared proposal.\"},{\"title\":\"PDF export\",\"description\":\"Generate a downloadable PDF version of any proposal, ready to send or archive.\"},{\"title\":\"Proposal versioning\",\"description\":\"Track changes over time with version numbers on each proposal.\"},{\"title\":\"Audit logging\",\"description\":\"Key actions are logged for accountability and traceability across your organization.\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive design across devices\",\"description\":\"Create, review, and adjust proposals on desktop, tablet, or mobile with a layout that adapts to your screen.\"},{\"title\":\"Authentication with email verification\",\"description\":\"Full signup, login, forgot password, and password reset flows with email-based authentication.\"}],\"content\":\"$45\",\"relativePath\":\"quotekit-proposal-quote-generator-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"creative-photographer\",\"id\":\"creative-photographer-portfolio\",\"title\":\"Visual gallery\",\"pageTitle\":\"Creative Photographer — Photography Portfolio Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"73480875-d5a8-4911-af79-566ef16c2894\",\"url\":\"https://creative-photographer.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Bold and creative photography portfolio template with dynamic layouts built with React and Tailwind CSS\",\"tagline\":\"Portfolio with image carousel\",\"description\":\"A vibrant photography portfolio template featuring bold layouts, creative compositions, and eye-catching 