cription\":\"Adaptive gallery layouts optimized for all devices with touch gestures and fluid image browsing\"},{\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance\",\"description\":\"Optimized image delivery with lazy loading, code splitting, and CDN-ready architecture for instant portfolio access\"},{\"title\":\"Premium UI Component Library\",\"description\":\"100+ pre-built components with Radix UI primitives for bold, creative, and professional presentation\"},{\"title\":\"SEO \u0026 Meta Optimization\",\"description\":\"Pre-configured meta tags, Open Graph cards, and structured data optimized for photography portfolio visibility\"},{\"title\":\"Accessibility Excellence (WCAG 2.1 AA)\",\"description\":\"Semantic HTML5, ARIA labels, and keyboard navigation ensuring all audiences can experience your creative work\"}],\"content\":\"$46\",\"relativePath\":\"creative-photographer.md\"},{\"slug\":\"retrofly-sprint-retrospective-board-template\",\"id\":\"retrofly-sprint-retrospective-board-template\",\"title\":\"Retrofly\",\"pageTitle\":\"Retrofly - Sprint Retrospective Board Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"638b3440-afc2-4cde-ba5b-95df4457d627\",\"url\":\"https://retrofly.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Asynchronous team retrospective and postmortem tool\",\"description\":\"Run async sprint retrospectives with structured feedback, upvoting, AI-powered summaries, and action item tracking. Two formats for detailed or lightweight retros.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Retrofly - Sprint Retrospective Board Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Run async sprint retrospectives with structured feedback, upvoting, AI-powered summaries, and action item tracking. Two formats for detailed or lightweight retros.\",\"subcategory\":\"project-management\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/retrofly.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/retrofly.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/retrofly.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"templates\",\"dashboard-templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"forum\",\"title\":\"Async feedback collection\",\"description\":\"Team members submit retro feedback on their own schedule. No meeting required, no scheduling conflicts, no dominating voices.\"},{\"icon\":\"tune\",\"title\":\"Two retro formats\",\"description\":\"Choose a detailed format with custom questions, timeline, top-three rankings, and structured insights, or a simple start/stop/continue board for faster cycles.\"},{\"icon\":\"thumb_up\",\"title\":\"Upvotes and comments\",\"description\":\"React to teammates' responses and discuss specifics. The most resonant feedback surfaces to the top naturally.\"},{\"icon\":\"auto_awesome\",\"title\":\"AI-powered summaries\",\"description\":\"One-click analysis of all responses with theme detection, sentiment breakdown, and a one-line takeaway.\"},{\"icon\":\"task_alt\",\"title\":\"Action item tracking\",\"description\":\"Follow-ups get assigned owners, due dates, and tracked statuses, tied directly to the retro that created them.\"},{\"icon\":\"folder_open\",\"title\":\"Team and project organization\",\"description\":\"Organize retros by team and project for long-term tracking. Filter and search across your retro history from the dashboard.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Async feedback collection\",\"description\":\"Team members contribute retro feedback on their own schedule with no meeting required.\"},{\"title\":\"Detailed retro format with custom questions and timeline\",\"description\":\"Structured retrospective with custom question editor, visual timeline, top-three highlights and concerns, and categorized insights.\"},{\"title\":\"Simple start/stop/continue format\",\"description\":\"Lightweight retro board for quick cycles when a full detailed retrospective isn't needed.\"},{\"title\":\"Visual timeline with collision-aware layout\",\"description\":\"Horizontal timeline with automatic overlap resolution, expandable entry cards, inline editing, and date range controls.\"},{\"title\":\"Upvotes on feedback entries\",\"description\":\"Team members react to each other's feedback so the most resonant points surface to the top.\"},{\"title\":\"Comments on responses\",\"description\":\"Discuss specific feedback items in comment threads without cluttering the main retro board.\"},{\"title\":\"Top-three highlights and concerns ranking\",\"description\":\"Each participant ranks their most important items, surfacing team-wide priorities automatically.\"},{\"title\":\"AI-powered summary with theme detection\",\"description\":\"One-click analysis identifies recurring themes across all team responses and produces an overall takeaway.\"},{\"title\":\"Sentiment analysis\",\"description\":\"AI evaluates the overall tone of feedback to give team leads a quick read on team morale and satisfaction.\"},{\"title\":\"AI-powered auto-grouping\",\"description\":\"Automatically cluster related response cards by theme, with AI-generated group names.\"},{\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop card grouping\",\"description\":\"Manually drag cards onto each other to create groups, or drag cards into existing groups to reorganize.\"},{\"title\":\"Action item tracking with ownership and due dates\",\"description\":\"Follow-ups get assigned owners, due dates, and tracked statuses, linked directly to the retro that created them.\"},{\"title\":\"Team and project organization\",\"description\":\"Group retrospectives by team and project so feedback stays organized and trackable over time.\"},{\"title\":\"Dashboard with search, filters, and sorting\",\"description\":\"Search retros by name, filter by project, team, or status, and sort by date or alphabetically.\"},{\"title\":\"Real-time collaboration and live updates\",\"description\":\"See teammates' contributions appear in real time as they add feedback, votes, comments, and action items.\"},{\"title\":\"One-click demo mode\",\"description\":\"Explore the full retrospective experience with sample feedback, votes, and action items before running your own.\"},{\"title\":\"Google and email authentication\",\"description\":\"Sign in with Google or email/password. Profile editing with display name and avatar.\"}],\"content\":\"$47\",\"relativePath\":\"retrofly-sprint-retrospective-board-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"editorial\",\"id\":\"96131d2c-ca5f-40e1-a193-6bbbf5c24be6\",\"title\":\"Architecture blog\",\"pageTitle\":\"Editorial — Architecture Blog Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"96131d2c-ca5f-40e1-a193-6bbbf5c24be6\",\"url\":\"https://modern-blog-70747.lovable.app/\",\"subtitle\":\"A sophisticated architecture blog template designed for architects and design professionals.\",\"tagline\":\"Editorial for group of writers\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated architecture blog template designed for architects and design professionals. Features elegant project showcases, high-quality image galleries, and clean typography perfect for architectural portfolios and design commentary.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Editorial - Architecture Blog Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Professional architecture blog template with project showcases and editorial layouts. Built with React and Tailwind CSS.\",\"subcategory\":\"blog\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Blog\",\"Architecture\",\"Design\",\"Portfolio\",\"Professional\"],\"screenshot\":\"/templates/editorial-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"/templates/editorial-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"/templates/previews/editorial-preview.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"is_partner_template\":false,\"date\":\"2025-10-28T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"stars\",\"title\":\"Editorial-Grade Design System\",\"description\":\"Professional typography, sophisticated color gradients, and premium layouts designed for modern content publishing\"},{\"icon\":\"gauge\",\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance\",\"description\":\"Optimized images, GPU-accelerated animations, and modern build tools deliver sub-2s load times\"},{\"icon\":\"devices\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Design\",\"description\":\"Touch-optimized layouts and fluid typography scale perfectly across phones, tablets, and desktops\"},{\"icon\":\"half_moon\",\"title\":\"Seamless Dark Mode\",\"description\":\"Automatic theme switching with system preference detection and smooth color transitions throughout\"},{\"icon\":\"newspaper\",\"title\":\"Built for Content Creators\",\"description\":\"Category filtering, social sharing, and rich article layouts designed for editorial storytelling\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Premium Typography System\",\"description\":\"Multi-weight Satoshi font with fluid type scaling and exceptional readability optimized for long-form content across all screen sizes\"},{\"title\":\"Interactive Content Galleries\",\"description\":\"Touch-enabled horizontal scroll galleries with snap points and smooth animations showcase featured articles with professional image layouts\"},{\"title\":\"Advanced Category Filtering\",\"description\":\"Real-time client-side filtering across seven content categories with sticky navigation and visual active states for seamless discovery\"},{\"title\":\"Sophisticated Color Gradients\",\"description\":\"Four-color gradient system with separate light and dark mode palettes creates distinctive brand identity with smooth hover animations\"},{\"title\":\"Professional Contact Forms\",\"description\":\"Validation-ready contact forms with loading states, toast notifications, and focus styling deliver polished user experiences\"},{\"title\":\"Scroll-Triggered Animations\",\"description\":\"IntersectionObserver-powered fade-in effects with staggered delays and customizable timing enhance storytelling without overwhelming users\"},{\"title\":\"Rich Article Components\",\"description\":\"Support for multiple blockquote styles, image captions, custom aspect ratios, and semantic HTML creates engaging editorial experiences\"},{\"title\":\"Social Media Integration\",\"description\":\"Built-in Facebook, Twitter, and LinkedIn sharing buttons with branded colors and responsive positioning drive content distribution\"},{\"title\":\"Accessibility-First Architecture\",\"description\":\"Semantic HTML5, ARIA labels, keyboard navigation, and AAA contrast ratios ensure content reaches all audiences\"},{\"title\":\"API-Ready Infrastructure\",\"description\":\"TanStack Query integration and component architecture enable seamless connection to headless CMS or custom backend systems\"},{\"title\":\"TypeScript Code Quality\",\"description\":\"Strict type checking, ESLint configuration, and modern React patterns ensure maintainable, production-ready code\"},{\"title\":\"Vite Build Optimization\",\"description\":\"SWC compilation, tree-shaking, and automatic code splitting deliver fast builds and optimized production bundles under 350KB\"}],\"content\":\"$48\",\"relativePath\":\"editorial.md\"},{\"slug\":\"roadmapper-product-roadmap-planner-template\",\"id\":\"roadmapper-product-roadmap-planner-template\",\"title\":\"Roadmapper\",\"pageTitle\":\"Roadmapper - Product Roadmap Planner Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"72aadf39-26a8-47f2-a75e-c7e121ed50d7\",\"url\":\"https://myroadmapcanvas.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Visual canvas and list view for planning upcoming features organized by quarter, status, or priority\",\"description\":\"Plan and track your product roadmap on a visual canvas. Organize features by quarter, assign statuses, collaborate with your team, and keep stakeholders aligned.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Roadmapper - Product Roadmap Planner Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Plan and track your product roadmap on a visual canvas. Organize features by quarter, assign statuses, collaborate with your team, and keep stakeholders aligned.\",\"subcategory\":\"product-management\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/roadmapper.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/roadmapper.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/roadmapper.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"templates\",\"dashboard-templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"view_kanban\",\"title\":\"Canvas and list views\",\"description\":\"Switch between a drag-and-drop canvas timeline and a sortable list view depending on how you want to manage your roadmap.\"},{\"icon\":\"task_alt\",\"title\":\"Feature cards with status tracking\",\"description\":\"Each item includes a title, description, status (planned, in progress, completed), priority level, and timeframe so stakeholders see progress at a glance.\"},{\"icon\":\"flag\",\"title\":\"Organize by quarter and priority\",\"description\":\"Group features by time horizon or business priority to match how your team plans.\"},{\"icon\":\"drag_indicator\",\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop reordering\",\"description\":\"Move items across the canvas timeline as plans evolve, with changes saved instantly.\"},{\"icon\":\"chat_bubble\",\"title\":\"Team collaboration with comments\",\"description\":\"Invite team members to your workspace, leave comments on roadmap items, and resolve discussions without another meeting.\"},{\"icon\":\"bar_chart\",\"title\":\"Built-in analytics dashboard\",\"description\":\"Track completion rates, status distribution, and priority breakdowns with built-in charts.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Canvas timeline view\",\"description\":\"Display your roadmap on a drag-and-drop canvas with features positioned along a timeline by quarter.\"},{\"title\":\"List view\",\"description\":\"Review all roadmap items in a sortable, scannable table format with status and priority columns.\"},{\"title\":\"Feature cards with status tracking\",\"description\":\"Each card shows title, description, owner, priority, and current status (planned, in progress, completed).\"},{\"title\":\"Drag-and-drop reordering\",\"description\":\"Move items across the canvas as priorities shift, with changes saved to the database instantly.\"},{\"title\":\"Priority levels\",\"description\":\"Assign low, medium, or high priority to each item to surface what matters most.\"},{\"title\":\"Inspector panel\",\"description\":\"Click any roadmap item to open a detail panel for editing title, description, status, priority, dates, and owner.\"},{\"title\":\"Inline comments\",\"description\":\"Leave comments on individual roadmap items to discuss scope, raise blockers, or provide updates.\"},{\"title\":\"Workspace management\",\"description\":\"Create workspaces, invite team members by email, and assign roles (admin, member, viewer).\"},{\"title\":\"Role-based access control\",\"description\":\"Admins can manage members and edit all items. Members can edit. Viewers have read-only access.\"},{\"title\":\"Analytics dashboard\",\"description\":\"Built-in charts showing status distribution, priority breakdowns, and completion metrics.\"},{\"title\":\"Keyboard shortcuts\",\"description\":\"Power-user shortcuts for common actions like adding items, switching views, and navigating the canvas.\"},{\"title\":\"Authentication\",\"description\":\"Email-based signup and login with password reset flow. Users verify their email before accessing the app.\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive design\",\"description\":\"Works on desktop, tablet, and mobile with adaptive layouts including a mobile inspector drawer.\"},{\"title\":\"Customizable branding\",\"description\":\"Apply your brand colors and typography using the design system so the roadmap feels like part of your product.\"}],\"content\":\"$49\",\"relativePath\":\"roadmapper-product-roadmap-planner-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"voyager\",\"id\":\"fec6356f-acc1-4974-862a-034e15cade27\",\"title\":\"Fashion magazine\",\"pageTitle\":\"Voyager — Modern Travel Blog Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"fec6356f-acc1-4974-862a-034e15cade27\",\"url\":\"https://voyager-blog.lovable.app/\",\"subtitle\":\"A beautifully designed fashion / travel magazine blog template perfect for explorers and adventure seekers.\",\"tagline\":\"Magazine-style company site\",\"description\":\"A beautifully designed travel blog template perfect for explorers and adventure seekers. Features responsive image galleries, destination guides, and engaging layouts ideal for travel bloggers, photographers, and digital nomads.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Voyager - Modern Travel Blog Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Modern travel blog template with beautiful galleries and destination layouts. Built with React and Tailwind CSS.\",\"subcategory\":\"blog\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Blog\",\"Travel\",\"Adventure\",\"Photography\",\"Lifestyle\"],\"screenshot\":\"/templates/voyager-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"/templates/voyager-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"/templates/previews/voyager-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#FFFFFF\",\"#1A1A1A\",\"#F5F5F5\",\"#8B9DC3\",\"#2C2C2C\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2025-10-28T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"image\",\"title\":\"Stunning Image Galleries\",\"description\":\"Professional photography layouts optimized for travel images and destination showcases\"},{\"icon\":\"trending_up\",\"title\":\"Lightning Fast\",\"description\":\"Optimized images, lazy loading, and code splitting for sub-2s load times worldwide\"},{\"icon\":\"compass\",\"title\":\"Destination-Ready Layouts\",\"description\":\"Purpose-built templates for itineraries, guides, and location-based content\"},{\"icon\":\"search\",\"title\":\"SEO-Optimized Structure\",\"description\":\"Structured data, semantic HTML5, and meta tags for maximum travel search visibility\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Premium Typography System\",\"description\":\"Multi-weight font pairings and fluid type scales for exceptional readability on any screen size\"},{\"title\":\"Visual Story Builder\",\"description\":\"Full-width image layouts, parallax effects, and gallery grids designed for immersive storytelling\"},{\"title\":\"SEO \u0026 Analytics Ready\",\"description\":\"Pre-configured meta tags, Open Graph cards, structured data, and analytics integration for maximum discoverability\"},{\"title\":\"Content Organization\",\"description\":\"Multi-category support, tag filtering, and intelligent search for easy content discovery\"},{\"title\":\"Performance Optimized\",\"description\":\"Image lazy loading, code splitting, and CDN-ready for lightning-fast load times\"},{\"title\":\"Accessibility First\",\"description\":\"WCAG 2.1 AA compliant with semantic HTML, ARIA labels, and keyboard navigation\"},{\"title\":\"Fully Responsive \u0026 Mobile-First\",\"description\":\"Fluid layouts optimized for phones, tablets, and desktops with touch gestures and breakpoint customization\"},{\"title\":\"Dark Mode Support\",\"description\":\"System-aware theme switching with smooth transitions\"}],\"content\":\"$4a\",\"relativePath\":\"voyager.md\"},{\"slug\":\"stackwise-inventory-management-system-template\",\"id\":\"stackwise-inventory-management-system-template\",\"title\":\"Stackwise\",\"pageTitle\":\"Stackwise - Inventory Management System Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"eaf13a24-9d23-4ea5-ae81-bd8ed9669775\",\"url\":\"https://stock-command-center-82.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Full-featured inventory management with AI-powered demand forecasting\",\"description\":\"Manage inventory with real-time stock tracking, supplier management, purchase orders, and AI-powered demand forecasting. Includes role-based access, barcode support, notifications, and analytics.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Stackwise - Inventory Management System Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Manage inventory with real-time stock tracking, supplier management, purchase orders, and AI-powered demand forecasting. Includes role-based access, barcode support, notifications, and analytics.\",\"subcategory\":\"internal-tools\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/stackwise.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/stackwise.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/stackwise.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"templates\",\"dashboard-templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"inventory_2\",\"title\":\"Real-time stock dashboard\",\"description\":\"See total SKUs, in-stock counts, low-stock warnings, and out-of-stock flags at a glance. A needs-attention section surfaces what requires action now.\"},{\"icon\":\"local_shipping\",\"title\":\"Purchase order workflow\",\"description\":\"Create and track purchase orders from draft through partial and full receiving. Stock updates automatically when shipments arrive.\"},{\"icon\":\"psychology\",\"title\":\"AI-powered reorder suggestions\",\"description\":\"Smart suggestions analyze consumption patterns and supplier lead times to recommend when and how much to reorder.\"},{\"icon\":\"query_stats\",\"title\":\"Demand forecasting\",\"description\":\"Project stock levels 30, 60, or 90 days out with visual charts that highlight when you'll dip below reorder thresholds.\"},{\"icon\":\"business\",\"title\":\"Supplier management\",\"description\":\"Maintain a directory with contact info, order history, lead times, and fulfillment accuracy scores for every supplier.\"},{\"icon\":\"manage_accounts\",\"title\":\"Role-based access control\",\"description\":\"Admins configure the system, managers handle day-to-day operations, and requestors browse and submit item requests.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Real-time stock dashboard\",\"description\":\"Metric cards show total SKUs, in-stock counts, low-stock warnings, and out-of-stock flags with live updates. A needs-attention section highlights items requiring action.\"},{\"title\":\"Product catalog with SKU, barcode, and categories\",\"description\":\"Central registry for every item with detailed attributes, pricing, and supplier links.\"},{\"title\":\"Custom fields for industry-specific needs\",\"description\":\"Admin-defined custom fields (text, number, boolean, date, select) let you track expiry dates, lot numbers, or any attribute your industry requires.\"},{\"title\":\"Stock movement audit trail\",\"description\":\"Every inventory change is logged with item, quantity, direction, timestamp, user, and reference notes.\"},{\"title\":\"Stock transfers between locations\",\"description\":\"Move inventory between warehouses, zones, or bins with tracked transfer movements and updated balances.\"},{\"title\":\"Purchase order workflow\",\"description\":\"Create, submit, and track purchase orders from draft through receiving with automatic stock updates.\"},{\"title\":\"Partial and full receiving\",\"description\":\"Mark items as partially or fully received against a purchase order, with stock adjusting automatically.\"},{\"title\":\"Supplier directory with performance metrics\",\"description\":\"Track supplier contacts, terms, order history, average lead times, and fulfillment accuracy in one place.\"},{\"title\":\"AI smart reorder suggestions\",\"description\":\"Analyze consumption patterns and supplier lead times to recommend optimized reorder thresholds and quantities.\"},{\"title\":\"Demand forecasting with 30/60/90-day projections\",\"description\":\"Project future stock levels with visual charts that highlight when items are expected to fall below threshold.\"},{\"title\":\"Anomaly detection\",\"description\":\"Automatically flag unusual movements like unexpected spikes, large adjustments, or sudden drops.\"},{\"title\":\"Natural language inventory search\",\"description\":\"Query inventory conversationally instead of clicking through filters.\"},{\"title\":\"Role-based access control\",\"description\":\"Three roles with distinct permissions — admins configure, managers operate, requestors browse and request.\"},{\"title\":\"Barcode support with printable labels\",\"description\":\"Generate and print barcode labels for items, and use quick-entry scan mode for faster stock movements.\"},{\"title\":\"Multi-location warehouse hierarchy\",\"description\":\"Organize inventory by warehouse, zone, aisle, shelf, and bin with transfer tracking between locations.\"},{\"title\":\"Inventory requests and approval workflow\",\"description\":\"Staff submit item requests that queue for manager approval, with status tracking through the full lifecycle.\"},{\"title\":\"Analytics — turnover, supplier performance, cost breakdown\",\"description\":\"Built-in reports for stock turnover rates, supplier lead times, spend by supplier, cost by category, and movement trends.\"},{\"title\":\"CSV import and export\",\"description\":\"Bulk import products, suppliers, and movements from CSV files, and export any dataset for external use.\"},{\"title\":\"Configurable notification system\",\"description\":\"Alerts for low stock, zero stock, PO reminders, overdue orders, and request updates with per-type toggle preferences.\"},{\"title\":\"Command palette with keyboard shortcuts\",\"description\":\"Press CMD+K (or Ctrl+K) to instantly search items, suppliers, orders, and navigate to any page.\"},{\"title\":\"Onboarding tour and guided walkthrough\",\"description\":\"First-time users get an interactive tooltip tour of key features and an optional step-by-step walkthrough of the core workflow.\"},{\"title\":\"Help center with searchable FAQ\",\"description\":\"Built-in help page with categorized, searchable FAQ covering getting started, inventory management, purchase orders, analytics, and settings.\"},{\"title\":\"One-click demo mode with seed data\",\"description\":\"Explore every feature with pre-loaded sample products, suppliers, movements, and purchase orders.\"}],\"content\":\"$4b\",\"relativePath\":\"stackwise-inventory-management-system-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"vesper\",\"id\":\"d2978eed-f6ef-4218-9f17-da78dfe6d5cc\",\"title\":\"Fashion blog\",\"pageTitle\":\"Vesper — Fashion Blog\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"a37d1d0d-556a-4b16-af20-d0385b80500f\",\"url\":\"https://vesper-blog.lovable.app/\",\"subtitle\":\"A sophisticated fashion blog template that combines editorial excellence with sustainable design principles.\",\"tagline\":\"Minimal, playful design\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated fashion blog template that combines editorial excellence with sustainable design principles. Perfect for fashion bloggers, style influencers, and brands committed to conscious fashion.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Vesper - Fashion Blog Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Elegant fashion blog template with editorial layouts and sustainable design focus. Built with React and Tailwind CSS.\",\"subcategory\":\"blog\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Blog\",\"Fashion\",\"Style\",\"Design\",\"Lifestyle\",\"Sustainable\"],\"screenshot\":\"/templates/vesper-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"/templates/vesper-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"/templates/previews/vesper-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#FAFAFA\",\"#1A1A1A\",\"#F5F5F5\",\"#2C2C2C\",\"#E8E8E8\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2025-10-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"image_stack\",\"title\":\"Editorial-Grade Fashion Design\",\"description\":\"High-fashion magazine aesthetic with vibrant colorful cards and dramatic typography system\"},{\"icon\":\"gauge\",\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance\",\"description\":\"CSS-only animations, static data architecture, and minimal JavaScript for sub-2s load times\"},{\"icon\":\"phone_iphone\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Layout\",\"description\":\"Adaptive grid system transforming 1 to 3 columns with immersive edge-to-edge mobile experience\"},{\"icon\":\"accessibility\",\"title\":\"Built for Accessibility\",\"description\":\"Semantic HTML, AAA contrast ratios, keyboard navigation, and screen reader optimized structure\"},{\"icon\":\"search\",\"title\":\"SEO-Ready Architecture\",\"description\":\"Prepared for dynamic meta tags, structured data, and social sharing optimization capabilities\"},{\"icon\":\"code\",\"title\":\"Extensible Modern Stack\",\"description\":\"React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS with Lovable Cloud integration ready for scaling\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Vibrant Color System\",\"description\":\"Eight distinct card colors for visual categorization with warm cream background and pure black typography for editorial sophistication and maximum readability\"},{\"title\":\"Premium Typography Hierarchy\",\"description\":\"Lora serif for body text and Supreme sans-serif for headings with responsive scaling from 11px to 120px for dramatic visual impact\"},{\"title\":\"Interactive Article Cards\",\"description\":\"Hover-transform effects with grayscale images and color overlays, aspect-ratio locked containers, and three-line excerpt clamping for consistent grid layouts\"},{\"title\":\"Featured Content Display\",\"description\":\"Hero-style split layout with responsive order reversal, larger typography, and prominent call-to-action for editorial curation and content prioritization\"},{\"title\":\"Newsletter Integration System\",\"description\":\"Controlled form with email validation, async submission handling, success toast notifications, and two design variants for conversion optimization throughout site\"},{\"title\":\"Progressive Content Loading\",\"description\":\"Load more pagination showing 6 articles initially, incrementing by 3 on click, maintaining scroll position for seamless mobile browsing experience\"},{\"title\":\"Related Articles Discovery\",\"description\":\"Contextual content recommendations on article pages with matching grid layout, encouraging deeper site engagement and extended reading sessions for visitors\"},{\"title\":\"Dark Mode Foundation\",\"description\":\"Complete CSS variable system with inverted color scheme defined and theme provider installed, ready for one-click activation with toggle component addition\"},{\"title\":\"Content Management Ready\",\"description\":\"TypeScript article interface with React Query configured, prepared for Lovable Cloud Supabase integration or headless CMS connection for dynamic content updates\"},{\"title\":\"Performance Optimized Images\",\"description\":\"Unsplash CDN integration with automatic compression and format conversion, aspect-ratio containers preventing layout shift, grayscale filter with blend-mode overlays\"},{\"title\":\"Developer-Quality Codebase\",\"description\":\"TypeScript strict mode, ESLint with React Hooks rules, Vite with SWC for 20x faster compilation, path aliases, and production-ready architecture\"},{\"title\":\"Social Sharing Prepared\",\"description\":\"Open Graph and Twitter Card meta tags defined, 1200x630 social images configured, ready for dynamic per-article metadata with React Helmet integration\"}],\"content\":\"$4c\",\"relativePath\":\"vesper.md\"},{\"slug\":\"triage-bug-report-form-tracker-template\",\"id\":\"triage-bug-report-form-tracker-template\",\"title\":\"Triage\",\"pageTitle\":\"Triage - Bug Report Form \u0026 Tracker Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"ef43fe19-bcb6-4b13-b021-5a72f7bae103\",\"url\":\"https://bugtrackr.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Standardized bug submission form with severity tracking and status dashboard\",\"description\":\"Track bugs from report to resolution with structured forms, severity levels, team assignment, and real-time dashboards. Built for engineering teams.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Triage - Bug Report Form \u0026 Tracker Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Track bugs from report to resolution with structured forms, severity levels, team assignment, and real-time dashboards. Built for engineering teams.\",\"subcategory\":\"developer-tools\",\"platform\":\"web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/bugtrackr.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/bugtrackr.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/lovable-assets/templates/bugtrackr.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"templates\",\"dashboard-templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-03-25T00:00:00.000000\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"bug_report\",\"title\":\"Structured bug submission form\",\"description\":\"Reporters fill in severity, steps to reproduce, expected vs. actual behavior, and environment details in a consistent format.\"},{\"icon\":\"dashboard\",\"title\":\"Real-time tracking dashboard\",\"description\":\"See all bugs organized by status — new, assigned, in progress, testing, resolved, and closed — updated live as changes happen.\"},{\"icon\":\"priority_high\",\"title\":\"Severity-based prioritization\",\"description\":\"Filter and sort by critical, high, medium, or low severity so your team focuses on the right issues first.\"},{\"icon\":\"group\",\"title\":\"Team assignment \u0026 roles\",\"description\":\"Assign bugs to team members, manage user roles (admin, moderator, user), and track who's working on what.\"},{\"icon\":\"history\",\"title\":\"Timestamped audit trail\",\"description\":\"Every report and status change logs who did it and when, creating an accountability trail for the full bug lifecycle.\"},{\"icon\":\"analytics\",\"title\":\"Analytics \u0026 reporting\",\"description\":\"Charts for severity distribution, status breakdown, resolution trends, and team velocity — built in, not bolted on.\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Structured bug submission form\",\"description\":\"Guided form with required fields that ensures every bug report contains the information your team needs to act.\"},{\"title\":\"Severity level classification\",\"description\":\"Reporters tag each bug as critical, high, medium, or low so your team can triage without guessing.\"},{\"title\":\"Steps to reproduce field\",\"description\":\"A dedicated section for step-by-step reproduction instructions so engineers can recreate issues reliably.\"},{\"title\":\"Expected vs. actual behavior fields\",\"description\":\"Side-by-side fields that clarify what should happen and what actually happens for faster diagnosis.\"},{\"title\":\"Analytics dashboard\",\"description\":\"Charts for severity distribution, status breakdown, daily trends, and resolution patterns — so you can measure and improve your process.\"},{\"title\":\"Open, in progress, and resolved views\",\"description\":\"Switch between filtered views to focus on bugs that need attention, are being worked on, or have been closed.\"},{\"title\":\"Severity-based filtering and sorting\",\"description\":\"Filter the dashboard by severity level to surface critical issues first during triage and standups.\"},{\"title\":\"Date-based sorting\",\"description\":\"Sort bugs by submission date to identify stale issues that have been sitting unresolved too long.\"},{\"title\":\"Timestamped entries with reporter details\",\"description\":\"Every report logs who submitted it and when, creating an accountability trail for the full bug lifecycle.\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive design across devices\",\"description\":\"Submit and review bug reports on desktop, tablet, or mobile with a layout that adapts to any screen size.\"}],\"content\":\"$4d\",\"relativePath\":\"triage-bug-report-form-tracker-template.md\"},{\"slug\":\"perspective-lifestyle\",\"id\":\"7410f81b-8218-4f2d-bb32-1ba1f84eabb2\",\"title\":\"Personal blog\",\"pageTitle\":\"Perspective - Lifestyle Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"af765f7c-2a17-4308-8692-b32f9c93f440\",\"url\":\"https://my-perspective-lifestyle.lovable.app/\",\"subtitle\":\"A sophisticated lifestyle blog template designed for wellness, travel, and personal growth content.\",\"tagline\":\"Muted, intimate design\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated lifestyle blog template designed for wellness, travel, and personal growth content. Features elegant layouts, inspiring design, and comprehensive content organization perfect for lifestyle influencers and educators.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Perspective - Lifestyle Blog Template | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Professional lifestyle blog template for wellness, travel, and personal growth. Built with React and Tailwind CSS.\",\"subcategory\":\"blog\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Blog\",\"Lifestyle\",\"Wellness\",\"Travel\",\"Personal Growth\",\"Content\"],\"screenshot\":\"https://pub-bb2e103a32db4e198524a2e9ed8f35b4.r2.dev/a8b116a9-20b6-43a8-ae91-693ba5a35c3b/id-preview-172571d0--7410f81b-8218-4f2d-bb32-1ba1f84eabb2.lovable.app-1760028648399.png\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://pub-bb2e103a32db4e198524a2e9ed8f35b4.r2.dev/a8b116a9-20b6-43a8-ae91-693ba5a35c3b/id-preview-172571d0--7410f81b-8218-4f2d-bb32-1ba1f84eabb2.lovable.app-1760028648399.png\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"/templates/previews/perspective-lifestyle-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#F5F1E8\",\"#3D3D3D\",\"#6B7280\",\"#4A3728\",\"#FAFAFA\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"is_partner_template\":false,\"date\":\"2025-10-09T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"stars\",\"title\":\"Editorial-Grade Design System\",\"description\":\"Premium typography and warm aesthetic optimized for content-focused blogs and publications\"},{\"icon\":\"newspaper\",\"title\":\"Content-First Architecture\",\"description\":\"Multi-section articles with categories, tags, and related content for superior discoverability\"},{\"icon\":\"half_moon\",\"title\":\"Built-in Dark Mode\",\"description\":\"Complete light and dark theme system with automatic detection and preference persistence\"},{\"icon\":\"gauge\",\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance\",\"description\":\"Vite-powered development with optimized builds, tree-shaking, and GPU-accelerated animations for sub-2s loads\"},{\"icon\":\"phone_iphone\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Design\",\"description\":\"Touch-optimized interactions and adaptive layouts across all devices from phones to desktops\"},{\"icon\":\"search\",\"title\":\"SEO \u0026 Accessibility Ready\",\"description\":\"WCAG AAA contrast ratios, semantic markup, and complete meta tag structure for discoverability\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Sophisticated Typography Hierarchy\",\"description\":\"Premium Google Fonts pairing of Inter and Merriweather with fluid responsive scaling for exceptional readability across all screen sizes\"},{\"title\":\"Category-Based Content Organization\",\"description\":\"Seven semantic categories with unique color coding, dedicated landing pages, and intelligent filtering for intuitive content discovery and navigation\"},{\"title\":\"Advanced Card Hover Effects\",\"description\":\"Dual-shadow elevation system with scale transforms and image zoom effects creating engaging, modern interactions that guide user attention\"},{\"title\":\"Related Content Engine\",\"description\":\"Automatic category-based article recommendations displayed in three-column grids to increase time-on-site and reduce bounce rates significantly\"},{\"title\":\"Social Sharing Integration\",\"description\":\"Platform-optimized share buttons for Twitter, Facebook, and LinkedIn with copy-link functionality and toast notifications for seamless content distribution\"},{\"title\":\"Newsletter Subscription Forms\",\"description\":\"Multiple strategically-placed email capture CTAs with rounded-full styling, ready for Mailchimp or ConvertKit integration to grow subscriber lists\"},{\"title\":\"TypeScript Full-Stack Foundation\",\"description\":\"Type-safe React components with strict interfaces and path aliases enabling confident refactoring, easy maintenance, and seamless CMS integration\"},{\"title\":\"Customizable Design Tokens\",\"description\":\"CSS variable-based color system and spacing scale allowing instant brand customization without touching component code or complex configurations\"},{\"title\":\"Author Attribution System\",\"description\":\"Rich author profiles with avatars and bios, creating credibility and personality while supporting multiple contributors for growing editorial teams\"},{\"title\":\"Glassmorphism UI Elements\",\"description\":\"Backdrop-blur floating buttons and semi-transparent overlays adding sophisticated depth and modern polish to category badges and navigation pills\"},{\"title\":\"Staggered Entry Animations\",\"description\":\"Progressive reveal animations with customizable delays creating cinematic page loads that feel premium and guide attention through content hierarchy\"},{\"title\":\"Production-Ready Deployment\",\"description\":\"Optimized Vite build pipeline with automatic code splitting, CSS purging, and static output ready for Vercel, Netlify, or any CDN\"}],\"content\":\"$4e\",\"relativePath\":\"perspective-lifestyle.md\"}]\n"])</s